{"tid":237800,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有兩副眼鏡以上既巴絲入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-05-10T15:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T12:08:56.000Z","uid":105220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db18b068e20a2cc61a19ed73873d3d88bc8f4ad0","tid":237800,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近我配多左副眼鏡 <br />\n兩副度數一樣想有時輪流戴下<br />\n<br />\n不過個款唔同 戴新個副眼鏡個時好唔慣<br />\n戴左幾個鐘先開始ok <br />\n但換返舊個副又要適應下<br />\n不停loop 對眼好攰<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日戴到我頭暈暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解有啲人可以適應得咁好<br />\n日日換都得<br />\n定係我唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3472dc238149a3169d13c46f94fb9a040e892416","tid":237800,"uid":13704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"811098921f6f584cd640529713ae6dffa4f020e4","tid":237800,"uid":50969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"你地去邊到買眼鏡多<br />\n開始度數唔岩 想換 求舖頭/牌子去睇睇"},{"pid":"0a4c0c6c369e730fa6b73c05614facd48e50cf03","tid":237800,"uid":48320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"係咪度數有問題<br />\n我6副出街 屋企一副 完全冇不適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f6774a9e072d6ca76e7e532a5be63eb1c1670c","tid":237800,"uid":13704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:29:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"541838a2b955c5d5ef77d8b329af780e13191914","tid":237800,"uid":48320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪度數有問題<br />\n我6副出街 屋企一副 完全冇不適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n副副類似形狀 鏡片大細差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n都唔算 有圓有方 44-51mm都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf8196q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf8196q.jpg&h=135ace32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d99c541feac83370a925091445e3f8e1953f68e2","tid":237800,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"我兩邊耳仔一高一低<br />\n新個副個感覺 好似斜左入去左邊少少<br />\n關唔關事？<br />\n但我搞個鼻托好耐都搞唔好...<br />\n我怕自己「咬」太多會斷"},{"pid":"6218883d1e28c4ac84786fb4cda2d05f2d95964c","tid":237800,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"有五副，各種型，大細都唔同<br />\n無試過暈<br />\n你暈既話可能係兩副焦點唔同"},{"pid":"c0236d701ad7498a307225fb250b45d5d25e23b0","tid":237800,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我兩邊耳仔一高一低<br />\n新個副個感覺 好似斜左入去左邊少少<br />\n關唔關事？<br />\n但我搞個鼻托好耐都搞唔好...<br />\n我怕自己「咬」太多會斷</blockquote><br />\n唔好自己調教，返去鋪頭啦。正常幾個月都應該返去一次整一整。"},{"pid":"7c0592def595c91c3bc982421f6f26ebf029e043","tid":237800,"uid":4214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪度數有問題<br />\n我6副出街 屋企一副 完全冇不適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n副副類似形狀 鏡片大細差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n都唔算 有圓有方 44-51mm都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf8196q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf8196q.jpg&h=135ace32&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想請問個眼鏡盒可以係邊度搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e0e6c3b9e410defe80c9bcce6bdc3675685703","tid":237800,"uid":48320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪度數有問題<br />\n我6副出街 屋企一副 完全冇不適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n副副類似形狀 鏡片大細差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n都唔算 有圓有方 44-51mm都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf8196q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf8196q.jpg&h=135ace32&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想請問個眼鏡盒可以係邊度搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼鏡鋪送 淘寶都有類似嘅"},{"pid":"414b72229d1b06e603e6dbe6138e5522c9ac334a","tid":237800,"uid":4214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪度數有問題<br />\n我6副出街 屋企一副 完全冇不適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n副副類似形狀 鏡片大細差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n都唔算 有圓有方 44-51mm都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf8196q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf8196q.jpg&h=135ace32&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想請問個眼鏡盒可以係邊度搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼鏡鋪送 淘寶都有類似嘅</blockquote><br />\n等我上淘寶搵搵先，thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8424d532ca9dc76ebab522e147ae11e47be3d9","tid":237800,"uid":41962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"鏡片牌子唔同 大細 新舊 鏡架角度  都可以令你唔舒服<br />\n高低當然都會 你可以拎埋舊個副去你配眼鏡個度比人睇睇 再較返差唔多可能會好啲"},{"pid":"c8cea51dc0e5a901d8b1c444fdeff6c4e8c6e88b","tid":237800,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏡片牌子唔同 大細 新舊 鏡架角度  都可以令你唔舒服<br />\n高低當然都會 你可以拎埋舊個副去你配眼鏡個度比人睇睇 再較返差唔多可能會好啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 我未必會再返去個間野先死 ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c11256323bac80dbb37537b4479bb65e1e9cef","tid":237800,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"我有12副眼鏡，日日唔同都無問題。"},{"pid":"0ecbd4b40e7b69b30ee1765723993d0a4bab2216","tid":237800,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係配鏡個時度數唔係幾準"},{"pid":"f2e6509e76d6e8c4a4b2351935807465c98e4caa","tid":237800,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,